  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether orale budesonide is effective in
      maintaining clinical remission in patients with collagenous colitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether orale budesonide is effective in
      maintaining clinical remission in patients with collagenous colitis.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
